u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F5%2F59%2FAuWaiLunfb2.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F185%3Fcb%3D20071006201801%22&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9kr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=628f5090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/5/59/AuWaiLunfb2.gif/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/185?cb=20071006201801&quot;</a>  /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n好耐冇睇過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d539918ed817078a17e5718bc1307e12471d77","tid":438761,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>單刀橫傳.gif</blockquote><br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/5/59/AuWaiLunfb2.gif/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/185?cb=20071006201801&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F5%2F59%2FAuWaiLunfb2.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F185%3Fcb%3D20071006201801%22&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9kr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=628f5090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/5/59/AuWaiLunfb2.gif/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/185?cb=20071006201801&quot;</a>  /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n好耐冇睇過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌, 睇左N年都咁好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276edd472b450d41d55c87ef8f9d1f14ad8701dc","tid":438761,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:57:57.000Z","msg":"而家都無人識前門神范俊業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecce29a476a632fee5c7ae2db676e29e7b9c91b6","tid":438761,"uid":74675,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"香港天才中鋒歐偉倫將會結束與南華多年關係轉投英超勁旅曼聯<br />\n<br />\n歐偉倫在02年香港賀歲杯中，一記美妙單刀橫傳，技驚四座。在本年三月，已傳出阿仙奴欲以亨利加三千萬磅買入此名香港前鋒，唯消息未經証實。本年十一月，曼聯高調表示為改善鋒力，必需購入一名二傳前鋒，收購目標直指倫仔！！<br />\n<br />\n曼聯球星雲尼斯達羅指出，十分期待與他練習。雲佬：「我看過他的比賽片段，真是妙極了！那記橫轉，我簡直呆了！他（歐）真是十分冷靜！」<br />\n<br />\n門將侯活亦為那記橫傳驚嘆！侯活：「如果當時把關的是我，我會不知如何是好，以為他會勁射，他竟出奇不意地作出橫傳！傳送位置更是我估不到的！」<br />\n<br />\n另外，曼聯隊教練費格遜表示：「我們用來買他的預算並沒有上限，我把房子賣了都可以，目的只為了他。我不惜用全部曼聯球員加上金錢來換取他一人！」<br />\n<br />\n對於南華有兩名主要華將離隊，梁守志被問及可會收購其他球員彌補球隊的損失。他表示對中田英壽及普波斯基有興趣，現在斟介中。<br />\n<br />\n最新橫濱消息：由於新加盟皇家馬德里的球星李健和未有於洲際杯上陣，導致球迷暴動。皇馬發言人表示，李健和未有上陣是為了保存體力以應付歐聯！另一方面，皇馬一眾球員如朗拿度，碧咸和費高等人卻表示感到憂慮，擔心正選位置不保。"},{"pid":"586e53e681f5a6a00f0ce53ad5184c98f051af8f","tid":438761,"uid":22227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T10:51:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81f228257bc1dd532a0128633ec95bf39c968bbd","tid":438761,"uid":133658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T10:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家都無人識前門神范俊業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日斬唔起龍門球<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a93f9a495b138b3602b96cfbf881b92904efbb","tid":438761,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T11:03:15.000Z","msg":"開始無人識陳七<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b8b3b6ca969359847c8ec35335adc02b0e99b0","tid":438761,"uid":27608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T11:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港天才中鋒歐偉倫將會結束與南華多年關係轉投英超勁旅曼聯<br />\n<br />\n歐偉倫在02年香港賀歲杯中，一記美妙單刀橫傳，技驚四座。在本年三月，已傳出阿仙奴欲以亨利加三千萬磅買入此名香港前鋒，唯消息未經証實。本年十一月，曼聯高調表示為改善鋒力，必需購入一名二傳前鋒，收購目標直指倫仔！！<br />\n<br />\n曼聯球星雲尼斯達羅指出，十分期待與他練習。雲佬：「我看過他的比賽片段，真是妙極了！那記橫轉，我簡直呆了！他（歐）真是十分冷靜！」<br />\n<br />\n門將侯活亦為那記橫傳驚嘆！侯活：「如果當時把關的是我，我會不